<refsection condition="ref.description">
<title>Description</title>

<para>The <tag>foreignphrase</tag> element can be used to markup the text
of a foreign word or phrase.
<quote>Foreign</quote> in this context means that it is a language
other than the primary language of the document and is not intended to
be pejorative in any way.
</para>

<refsection><title>Processing expectations</title>
<para>A <tag>foreignphrase</tag> is often given special typographic
treatment, such as italics.
</para>
</refsection>

